item.title: 【Requests】[REQ AUD] - RQ Various Britney Spears Lossless Stems
item.description:
Hi!
I had all these YEARS ago when they first leaked, but I can't find them in lossless anymore someone downscaled them all. Can someone please re-upload the lossless stems for:
Scary
He About To Lose Me
How I Roll
Don't Keep Me Waiting
Up N Down
I Wanna Go
Criminal
Hold It Against Me (regular stems+ dry vocal stems [I hate that I lost them!])
Drop Dead (Beautiful)
Lace & Leather
Toxic
Til The World Ends
Slave 4 U


If you have any of these I would be so grateful! It's unfortunate people downscaled them to 128kbps & that's what's common online like any good remixes could be made with them. I don't think Selfish, TTYH, Inside Out, or Seal It With A Kiss ever surfaced but if they did I would also be grateful for them! Honestly if anyone wants to drop drop whatever lossless Britney stems they have I'm sure this would become an amazing resource for someone in the future.
Thank you so much!
